h flaked almonds or pearl sugar after brushing with egg.","One minute before the end of the kneading in <b>step 2,<b> add <b>80 g raisins.<b>","Form dough into small men. Use raisins for eyes and buttons."],"basicInfo":["medium","20m","2h 20m","30 slices"]}